overview:
Morrow Kidman Tinker is a law firm representing adults and children who have been injured by negligent conduct and defective products. We have fought and won on behalf of hundreds of seriously injured clients in nearly every county in Washington.

If you or a loved one has been injured by someone’s negligence, our mission is to hold them accountable for the consequences. Our lawyers have earned one of the state’s top reputations for successfully recovering money damages for our clients. Visit our website to see a sampling of our successful cases.
